gs with this release and it is recommended that you do not<br \/>\nfile bug reports against the packages in this release. If you come across any<br \/>\nissue which may be packaging related, it is recommended that you join the<br \/>\nKubuntu KDE 4 IRC channel (#kubuntu-kde4) and query those in the channel.\n<\/p>\n<p>Thanks to Harald <em>&#8220;apachelogger&#8221;<\/em> Sitter for preparing these packages.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>KDE 4.1 RC 1 has been released and packages are available for Kubuntu 8.04, the Hardy Heron. These packages install to \/usr\/lib\/kde4 and can be installed along side your existing KDE 3 installation. Notes This is a release candidate quality package and may yet prove to be unstable at times&#8230;.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[129],"tags":[142,144,178],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/719"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=719"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/719\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1510,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/719\/revisions\/1510"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=719"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=719"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=719"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}